24175%20million%20Frank%20sale%20herself%2C%20while%20her%20defense%20lawyers%20put%20the%20figure%20closer%20to%20%2421%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20more%20about%20Charlie%20Javice%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-verdict-frank-startup-guilty-jpmorgan-fraud-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Javice%20verdict%3A%20Frank%20founder%20is%20guilty%20in%20%24175%20million%20defrauding%20of%20JPMorgan%20Chase%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-trial-closings-one-word-will-play-starring-role-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOne%20word%20played%20a%20starring%20role%20in%20the%20closing%20arguments%20of%20Frank%20founder%20Charlie%20Javice's%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-frank-fintech-startup-jp-morgan-fraud-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEveryone%20bought%20Charlie%20Javice's%20pitch.%20Nobody%20asked%20the%20right%20questions.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20Chase%20had%20seen%20great%20marketing%20potential%20in%20Frank's%20massive%20database%20of%204%20million%20users%2C%20according%20to%20trial%20testimony.%20The%20bank%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20contact%20information%20to%20pitch%20checking%20accounts%2C%20credit%20cards%2C%20and%20other%20banking%20products%20to%20college-age%20users%20at%20the%20start%20of%20their%20lifelong%20financial%20journeys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20defendant's%20lies%2C%20JPMC%20projected%20it%20could%20generate%20more%20than%20%24500%20million%20in%20revenue%20from%20selling%20banking%20products%20to%20Frank's%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20JPMC%20known%20the%20truth%20%E2%80%94%20that%20Frank%20had%20only%20a%20few%20hundred%20thousand%20users%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bank%