epairs%20have%20soared%2C%20but%20services%20are%20getting%20less%20availability%20in%20return.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Army%20and%20Marine%20Corps%20are%20struggling%20to%20maintain%20their%20combat%20vehicle%20fleets%20and%20keep%20them%20ready%20for%20war%2C%20with%20shortages%20of%20spare%20parts%20and%20maintainers%20sidelining%20many%20of%20them%2C%20a%20US%20government%20watchdog%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gao.gov%2Fproducts%2Fgao-25-108679%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20last%20week%20examined%20nearly%20a%20decade%20of%20data%2C%20finding%20that%20of%2018%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20including%20tanks%2C%20self-propelled%20artillery%2C%20and%20armored%20personnel%20carriers%20%E2%80%94%2016%20were%20not%20sufficiently%20mission%20capable%2C%20or%20available%20for%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20and%20Marine%20Corps%20spent%20over%20%242.3%20billion%20combined%20on%20high-level%20ground%20vehicle%20maintenance%2C%20according%20to%20the%20GAO%20report.%20Despite%20these%20investments%2C%20vehicle%20readiness%20plummeted%20due%20to%20insufficient%20numbers%20of%20trained%20mechanics%20and%20diminished%20manufacturing%20sources%20for%20repair%20parts%2C%20with%20single-source%20suppliers%20often%20becoming%20chokepoints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watchdog%20report%20highlighted%20the%20limitations%20of%20vehicle%20availability%20for%20any%20potential%20mission%2C%20noting%20that%20mission-capable%20rates%20have%20declined%20since%202015.%20None%20of%20the%20Army%20vehicles%20that%20inspectors%20looked%20at%20met%20the%20Army's%20goal%20of%20being%20ready%20to%20support%20a%20mission%2090%25%20of%20the%20time%20in%20FY%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GAO%20reported%20that%20between%20fiscal%20years%202015%20and%202024%2C%20per-vehicle%20maintenance%20costs%20for%20the%20Abrams%20tank%20more%20than%20doubled%20while%20availability%20rates%20were%20well%20below%20target.%20Fleet-wide%20maintenance%20costs%20for%20the%20Army%20surged%20almost%2050%25%20during%20this%20window.%20That%20figure%20dropped%20for%20the%20Corps%2C%20but%20per-vehicle%20repair%20costs%20for%20a%20handful%20of%20vehicles%20jumped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20military%20vehicles%20studied%20were%20also%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-stryker-vehicles-help-ukraine-recapture-lost-territory-kharkiv-report-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStryker%20Combat%20Vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-inside-ukraine-us-bradley-fighting-vehicles-troops-alive-russia-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBradley%20Fighting%20Vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Joint%20Light%20Tactical%20Vehicles%2C%20key%20elements%20of%20specific%20Army%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-combat-brigades-switch-to-armor-to-prepare-for-great-power-fight-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebrigade%20combat%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Each%20is%20a%20rugged%20vehicle%20equipped%20with%20varied%20armaments%20and%20capable%20of%20moving%20troops%20across%20battlefields%20using%20wheels%20or%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFive%20of%20six%20selected%20Army%20ground%20combat%20vehicles%20did%20not%20meet%20mission%20capable%20goals%20in%20any%20fiscal%20year%20during%20the%20time%20frame%20of%20GAO's%20review%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20Over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20%26quot%3Bselected%20Army%20ground%20support%20vehicles%20achieved%20mission%20capable%20goals%20about%2020%20percent%20of%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20and%20Marine%20Corps%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExtensive%20depot%20overhauls%20have%20collapsed%2C%20falling%20from%201%2C278%20in%202015%20to%20just%2012%20in%202024%20while%20the%20Mar