%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpost%2Fpreview%3Fsvapi%3D%26post_id%3D68cd8300a0c50753c2bdd0a8%26bust-capi%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Resiliency%20Playbook%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20event%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20show%20that%20you've%20stored%20it%2C%20you're%20getting%20paid%20to%20store%20it%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20show%20that%20it's%20measurable%20and%20verifiable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20buyers%20like%20Microsoft%2C%20that%20means%20carbon%20credits%20coming%20from%20land%20that%20Dell's%20team%20owns%20and%20manages.%20Microsoft's%20deal%20is%20expected%20to%20result%20in%207%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20US-based%20carbon%20removal%20credits%20over%20a%2025-year%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20buyer%20comes%20to%20us%2C%20we%20commit%20to%20them%20that%20we're%20selling%20the%20carbon%20units%20out%20of%20that%20forest.%20They%20can%20see%20it%2C%20we%20own%20it.%20They%20know%20it's%20there%20in%20perpetuity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarbon%20credits%20aren't%20new.%20Each%20token%20represents%20the%20equivalent%20of%201%20metric%20ton%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20reduced%20or%20removed%20from%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20through%20projects%20like%20tree%20planting%20and%20air%20capture.%20It's%20a%20way%20for%20companies%20to%20show%20that%20they're%20working%20to%20soften%20their%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20demand%20surged%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20questions%20have%20been%20raised%20around%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceezer-11-million-hv-capital-carbon-credits-transparent-pitch-deck-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equality%20of%20carbon%20credits%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20said%20he%20knows%20from%20experience%20how%20challenging%20it%20can%20be%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions.%20His%20firm%2C%20Kimmeridge%2C%20set%20out%20to%20have%20net-zero%20emissions%2C%20and%20he%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20difficult%26quot%3B%20to%20find%20high-quality%20carbon%20removal%20credits.%20That%20inspired%20Dell's%20work%20with%20Chestnut%2C%20which%20began%20about%20three%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChestnut%20has%20planted%20trees%20in%20almost%2030%2C000%20acres%20of%20land%20across%20Louisiana%2C%20Alabama%2C%20and%20Mississippi%2C%20Dell%20said.%20The%20company%20has%20purchased%20a%20total%20of%2060%2C000%20acres%20that%20will%20eventually%20be%20restored.%20Parts%20of%20Chestnut's%20property%20are%20open%20to%20local%20communities%20who%20use%20the%20land%20for%20hunting%20and%20fishing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20go%20and%20see%20our%20properties%20over%20time%2C%20they%20essentially%20look%20like%20national%20forests%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20scaling%20isn't%20easy.%20Dell%20said%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20in%20running%20the%20organization%20is%20sourcing%20the%20trees%20themselves.%20Chestnut%20is%20focused%20on%20restoring%20land%20with%20native%20hardwoods%2C%20which%20have%20been%20difficult%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20the%20largest%20buyer%20of%20hardwood%20seedlings%20and%20saplings%20in%20the%20southeast%20%5BUS%5D%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Dell%20said.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20nurseries%20are%20not%20designed%20for%20hardwood%20species.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20said%20Chestnut%20is%20partnering%20with%20nurseries%20across%20the%20US%20to%20build%20a%20more%20reliable%20supply%20chain.%20Still%2C%20Dell%20acknowledges%20the%20challenges%20companies%20face%20in%20meeting%20their%20emissions%20goals%20with%20the%20current%20options%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20sector%20where%20people%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20pontificating%20and%20there's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Dell%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20industry%20got%20together%20and%20actually%20started%20to%20make%20things%20happen%2C%20we'd%20get%20a%20lot%20further.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fben-dell-explains-chestnut-carbon-microsoft-carbon-credit-deal-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759176165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d9bca95dbc4fd10da9ba20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fben-dell-explains-chestnut-carbon-microsoft-carbon-credit-deal-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Big%20power%20users%20like%20Microsoft%20and%20the%20Mercedes%20F1%20team%20are%20buying%20carbon%20credits%20despite%20the%20questions%20surrounding%20the%20practice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart%2CKim%20Last)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fben-dell-explains-chestnut-carbon-microsoft-carbon-credit-deal-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20expected%20the%20Ryder%20Cup%20to%20be%20one%20big%20frat%20party.%20The%20level%20of%20corporate%20polish%20caught%20me%20by%20surprise.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225865%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryder%20Cup%20Friday%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d9975fcc993f9955cf1167%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223910%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20went%20to%20the%20Ryder%20Cup%20on%20Friday%20and%20saw%20the%20role%20of%20corporate%20America%20more%20clearly%20than%20most%20else.%3Cp%3EScott%20Taetsch%2FPGA%20of%20America%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20the%20Ryder%20Cup%20on%20Friday%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20th