only%26quot%3B%20at%2011%3A40%2C%20which%20still%20had%20pee%20all%20over%20the%20seat%20and%20no%20toilet%20paper.%20A%20woman%20behind%20me%20mumbled%20to%20herself%20about%20the%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227579%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BMW%20House%20Ryder%20Cup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dab0085dbc4fd10da9c41b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225055%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20the%20sponsors'%20areas%20offered%20prime%20views.%3Cp%3EMike%20Stobe%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20official%20sponsors%20and%20suppliers'%20names%20dotted%20nearly%20every%20sign%20and%20experience.%20I%20overheard%20a%20few%20conversations%20about%20deals%20and%20prices%2C%20but%20the%20real%20networking%20seemed%20to%20take%20place%20mainly%20in%20the%20corporate%20hospitality%20tents.%20Cerasoli%20said%20the%20event%20is%20key%20to%20maintaining%20strong%20relationships%2C%20and%20that%20some%20legitimate%20business%20talk%20is%20sprinkled%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECerasoli%20and%20I%20spoke%20from%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20set%20of%20bleachers%20reserved%20for%20guests%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BWorldwide%20Partners%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20offered%20a%20prime%20view%20of%20the%20first%20and%20last%20holes.%20He%20didn't%20share%20how%20much%20Citi%20spent%20on%20the%20Ryder%20Cup%20(%26quot%3Benough%26quot%3B)%20or%20how%20many%20tickets%20they%20gave%20out%20(%26quot%3Bnot%20enough%26quot%3B)%2C%20but%20said%20that%20this%20tournament%20is%20geared%20toward%20the%20upper%20echelons%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryder-cup-golf-private-jets-new-york-celebrities-trump-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewealth%20and%20institutional%20clients%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20invested%20at%20a%20level%20that%20reflects%20how%20important%20this%20partnership%20is%20to%20our%20clients%20and%20our%2